
AI Resume Screening System
📌 Overview

This project is an AI-powered Resume Screening System built using LangChain and Gemini.

It evaluates a candidate's resume based on a given job description and provides:

Skill extraction
Matching analysis
Score (0–100)
Explanation

--> Tech Stack
Python
LangChain
Gemini API
LangSmith

How to Run
Install dependencies:
pip install langchain langchain-core langchain-google-genai python-dotenv
Add API key in .env:
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_api_key
Run the project:
python main.py
